_meta.description: Skill training method definitions. IDs reference ObjectID, NpcID, and ItemID from RuneLite API.
_meta.id_strategy: Object/NPC IDs are automatically expanded via CollectionResolver at runtime. Only representative IDs are needed - if an ID exists in ObjectCollections or NpcCollections, the entire collection is used automatically.
_meta.example: targetObjectIds: [10820] expands to all 17+ oak tree variants via OAK_TREES collection
